data.description: Experience modern luxury living at its finest in the highly sought-after LC Communities! This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath condo with a 2-car attached garage offers a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover a spacious open-concept living area, ideal for hosting gatherings or relaxing in style. The kitchen comes with stainless steel appliances, countertops, and ample cabinet space and formal dining room. The property features a full basement with a finished rec room area, providing additional space for recreation or entertainment. Outside, a private patio area perfect for enjoying the outdoors in privacy. Residents enjoy exclusive access to a range of amenities, including The Goat Restaurant, a sparkling pool, clubhouse, fitness facility, bike and walking paths.
